title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1985-06-14
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi DR-1/Dolby B) -> Sound Devices 744T (24bit/96k) -> Samplitude Professional v10.22 -> FLAC/16
description:
Set 1

Dancin' In The Streets, West L.A. Fadeaway, CC Rider, Peggy-O, Hell In A Bucket, Keep On Growing-> Stagger Lee-> Let It Grow-> Deal

Set 2

Morning Dew-> Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Smokestack Lightning-> Comes A Time-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Day Job

Equipment problems after bucket caused them to leave the stage for a while

reviews.review_text:
Flag Day in a City That Don't Like the Flag Oh, well. That's okay, I guess, but I'd be a real flag waver if'n the lads had done U.S. Blues that day. Sadly, they didn't, but it didn't matter.

This is a well-recorded version of a well-played show. Rango AUD pretty sweet, as usual.

Lively second set. Have to give this performance a 4.5 and that's good enough. Nothing to write home about, but we ran out of paper long before we got there.
